{
  "video_id": "5ITyd1Pzek0",
  "title": "How to Enrich a Country: Free Trade or Protectionism?",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 63.0,
      "end_time": 3437.0,
      "text": "One of the most pressing choices facing modern economies"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 3437.0,
      "end_time": 4341.0,
      "text": "is whether to adopt"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 4341.0,
      "end_time": 6566.0,
      "text": "a policy of free trade"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 6566.0,
      "end_time": 8656.0,
      "text": "or of protectionism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 8656.0,
      "end_time": 10221.0,
      "text": "that is, whether to encourage"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 10221.0,
      "end_time": 12063.0,
      "text": "foreign goods into the country with"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 12063.0,
      "end_time": 13327.0,
      "text": "minimum tariffs"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 13327.0,
      "end_time": 15792.0,
      "text": "and allow industries to relocate abroad;"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 15792.0,
      "end_time": 18292.0,
      "text": "or whether to make it hard for foreign firms"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 18292.0,
      "end_time": 20208.0,
      "text": "to sell their goods internally"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 20208.0,
      "end_time": 22632.0,
      "text": "and discourage domestic producers"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 22632.0,
      "end_time": 25938.0,
      "text": "tempted by cheaper wages in other lands."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 25938.0,
      "end_time": 28440.0,
      "text": "It feels like a very modern dilemma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 28440.0,
      "end_time": 31292.0,
      "text": "but the debates between proponents of free trade"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 31292.0,
      "end_time": 32595.0,
      "text": "and protectionism"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 32595.0,
      "end_time": 34963.0,
      "text": "go back a very long way."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 34963.0,
      "end_time": 38718.0,
      "text": "The argument began in earnest in Europe in the 15th century"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 38718.0,
      "end_time": 40498.0,
      "text": "with the formulation of a theory"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 40498.0,
      "end_time": 42389.0,
      "text": "known as mercantilism"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 42389.0,
      "end_time": 44684.0,
      "text": "the forerunner of what we today"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 44684.0,
      "end_time": 47473.0,
      "text": "refer to as protectionism."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 47473.0,
      "end_time": 51390.0,
      "text": "Mercantilism was, like nearly every economic theory"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 51390.0,
      "end_time": 54338.0,
      "text": "interested in increasing a nation’s wealth."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 54338.0,
      "end_time": 56054.0,
      "text": "But, Mercantilists argued"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 56054.0,
      "end_time": 57651.0,
      "text": "that in order to grow richer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 57651.0,
      "end_time": 58890.0,
      "text": "a country had to try"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 58890.0,
      "end_time": 60702.0,
      "text": "to make as many things as possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 60702.0,
      "end_time": 62641.0,
      "text": "within its own borders"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 62641.0,
      "end_time": 64919.0,
      "text": "Nd reduce to an absolute minimum"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 64919.0,
      "end_time": 67884.0,
      "text": "any reliance on foreign imports."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 67884.0,
      "end_time": 68988.0,
      "text": "The role of government"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 68988.0,
      "end_time": 70577.0,
      "text": "was to help local industries"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 70577.0,
      "end_time": 73168.0,
      "text": "by applying huge tariffs on imported goods"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 73168.0,
      "end_time": 75623.0,
      "text": "and discouraging foreign manufacturers"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 75623.0,
      "end_time": 78546.0,
      "text": "from competing with local players."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 78546.0,
      "end_time": 80747.0,
      "text": "A strong country was one that knew how to"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 80747.0,
      "end_time": 82049.0,
      "text": "provide for itself"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 82049.0,
      "end_time": 85020.0,
      "text": "and could achieve almost total independence in trade"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 85020.0,
      "end_time": 86124.0,
      "text": "a goal known as"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 86124.0,
      "end_time": 86814.0,
      "text": "economic"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 86814.0,
      "end_time": 88287.0,
      "text": "economic autarky."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 88287.0,
      "end_time": 90900.0,
      "text": "The philosophy of mercantilism reigned supreme"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 90900.0,
      "end_time": 93244.0,
      "text": "as the most persuasive theory of economics"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 93244.0,
      "end_time": 96644.0,
      "text": "until the 9th of March 1776"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 96644.0,
      "end_time": 98599.0,
      "text": "the publication date of possibly"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 98599.0,
      "end_time": 100210.0,
      "text": "the most important book"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 100210.0,
      "end_time": 102890.0,
      "text": "in the history of the modern world."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 102890.0,
      "end_time": 107505.0,
      "text": "In &#39;An Inquiry into the Nature and Causes of the Wealth of Nations&#39;"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 107505.0,
      "end_time": 110199.0,
      "text": "the Scottish philosopher and economist Adam Smith"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 110199.0,
      "end_time": 111754.0,
      "text": "attempted to dynamite"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 111754.0,
      "end_time": 114664.0,
      "text": "the intellectual underpinnings of mercantilism."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 114664.0,
      "end_time": 116538.0,
      "text": "Smith argued that the best way for"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 116538.0,
      "end_time": 118127.0,
      "text": "any country to grow wealthy"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 118127.0,
      "end_time": 121147.0,
      "text": "was not to try to make everything by itself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 121147.0,
      "end_time": 122633.0,
      "text": "for no country could ever hope"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 122633.0,
      "end_time": 125613.0,
      "text": "to do well in every sector of an economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 125613.0,
      "end_time": 126566.0,
      "text": "Smith observed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 126566.0,
      "end_time": 128114.0,
      "text": "that countries naturally had"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 128114.0,
      "end_time": 130673.0,
      "text": "different strengths in particular areas"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 130673.0,
      "end_time": 132435.0,
      "text": "Some were great at making wine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 132435.0,
      "end_time": 134214.0,
      "text": "others had talent in pottery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 134214.0,
      "end_time": 136822.0,
      "text": "others still might be experts at making lace"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 136822.0,
      "end_time": 138307.0,
      "text": "and it was on such strengths"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 138307.0,
      "end_time": 140913.0,
      "text": "that every country should focus."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 140913.0,
      "end_time": 142256.0,
      "text": "This was an application"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 142256.0,
      "end_time": 143772.0,
      "text": "at the level of nations"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 143772.0,
      "end_time": 145934.0,
      "text": "of a theory we can understand well enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 145934.0,
      "end_time": 148501.0,
      "text": "at the level of individual life."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 148501.0,
      "end_time": 150494.0,
      "text": "If someone has a natural aptitude"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 150494.0,
      "end_time": 151582.0,
      "text": "for accountancy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 151582.0,
      "end_time": 153147.0,
      "text": "it makes no sense for them to spend"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 153147.0,
      "end_time": 154977.0,
      "text": "a considerable part of each day"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 154977.0,
      "end_time": 156955.0,
      "text": "trying also to make cheese,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 156955.0,
      "end_time": 158224.0,
      "text": "to sew their own trousers"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 158224.0,
      "end_time": 160188.0,
      "text": "or to learn to play violin sonatas."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 160188.0,
      "end_time": 161690.0,
      "text": "Far better for the accountant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 161690.0,
      "end_time": 162515.0,
      "text": "cheese-maker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 162515.0,
      "end_time": 163977.0,
      "text": "tailor and violinist"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 163977.0,
      "end_time": 165805.0,
      "text": "to specialize in the areas in which"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 165805.0,
      "end_time": 168030.0,
      "text": "they each have the greatest advantage"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 168030.0,
      "end_time": 169809.0,
      "text": "and then trade with others to"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 169809.0,
      "end_time": 172249.0,
      "text": "satisfy their remaining needs."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 172249.0,
      "end_time": 173431.0,
      "text": "As Smith noted:"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 173431.0,
      "end_time": 174956.0,
      "text": "“It is the maxim of every"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 174956.0,
      "end_time": 176832.0,
      "text": "prudent master of a family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 176832.0,
      "end_time": 179231.0,
      "text": "never to attempt to make at home"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 179231.0,
      "end_time": 180653.0,
      "text": "what it will cost him more"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 180653.0,
      "end_time": 183302.0,
      "text": "to make than to buy.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 183302.0,
      "end_time": 185383.0,
      "text": "Smith emphasized that if Britain could"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 185383.0,
      "end_time": 187345.0,
      "text": "produce woolen goods more cheaply"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 187345.0,
      "end_time": 188053.0,
      "text": "than Portugal"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 188053.0,
      "end_time": 189649.0,
      "text": "and if Portugal could produce"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 189649.0,
      "end_time": 191557.0,
      "text": "wine more cheaply than Britain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 191557.0,
      "end_time": 193893.0,
      "text": "then it would be beneficial to both parties"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 193893.0,
      "end_time": 195418.0,
      "text": "to exchange the product they"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 195418.0,
      "end_time": 196991.0,
      "text": "could make at a lower cost"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 196991.0,
      "end_time": 198493.0,
      "text": "for the one they could only make"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 198493.0,
      "end_time": 200035.0,
      "text": "at a higher cost."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 200035.0,
      "end_time": 202378.0,
      "text": "The overall wealth of both countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 202378.0,
      "end_time": 204546.0,
      "text": "would rise as labor and capital"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 204546.0,
      "end_time": 206652.0,
      "text": "would always be optimally employed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 206652.0,
      "end_time": 208393.0,
      "text": "directed to those sectors"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 208393.0,
      "end_time": 210489.0,
      "text": "where native skill and opportunity"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 210489.0,
      "end_time": 212206.0,
      "text": "was at its greatest."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 212206.0,
      "end_time": 213438.0,
      "text": "The job of the government"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 213438.0,
      "end_time": 214938.0,
      "text": "was to recognise sectors where"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 214938.0,
      "end_time": 216741.0,
      "text": "there was a national advantage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 216741.0,
      "end_time": 219016.0,
      "text": "assist in the education of the workforce,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 219016.0,
      "end_time": 220737.0,
      "text": "but otherwise, reduce tariffs"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 220737.0,
      "end_time": 221986.0,
      "text": "as much as possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 221986.0,
      "end_time": 223448.0,
      "text": "and step out of the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 223448.0,
      "end_time": 224815.0,
      "text": "With astonishing speed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 224815.0,
      "end_time": 227069.0,
      "text": "Smith’s theory convinced most of the economic"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 227069.0,
      "end_time": 228293.0,
      "text": "and political classes of"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 228293.0,
      "end_time": 229852.0,
      "text": "north Western Europe."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 229852.0,
      "end_time": 231209.0,
      "text": "In Britain, his ideas were"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 231209.0,
      "end_time": 233152.0,
      "text": "first put to a practical test"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 233152.0,
      "end_time": 235272.0,
      "text": "in relation to the primary foodstuff"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 235272.0,
      "end_time": 236352.0,
      "text": "of the nation:"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 236352.0,
      "end_time": 237545.0,
      "text": "corn."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 237545.0,
      "end_time": 239419.0,
      "text": "Grain prices had, for many years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 239419.0,
      "end_time": 241676.0,
      "text": "been protected by government decrees."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 241676.0,
      "end_time": 244560.0,
      "text": "Cheaper foreign grain had been kept out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 244560.0,
      "end_time": 246022.0,
      "text": "apparently in order to"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 246022.0,
      "end_time": 248716.0,
      "text": "protect jobs and national wealth."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 248716.0,
      "end_time": 250194.0,
      "text": "But Smith’s ideas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 250194.0,
      "end_time": 251924.0,
      "text": "now driven forward by his foremost"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 251924.0,
      "end_time": 253839.0,
      "text": "disciple David Ricardo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 253839.0,
      "end_time": 256914.0,
      "text": "proposed that all tariffs on imported grain"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 256914.0,
      "end_time": 258431.0,
      "text": "protectionist measures known as"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 258430.99999999997,
      "end_time": 259939.99999999997,
      "text": "The Corn Laws"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 259940.0,
      "end_time": 262998.0,
      "text": "were in fact obstacles to economic growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 262998.0,
      "end_time": 264937.0,
      "text": "After bitter debates in Parliament,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 264937.0,
      "end_time": 267871.0,
      "text": "the laws were repealed in 1846."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 267871.0,
      "end_time": 269602.0,
      "text": "The result demonstrated both"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 269602.0,
      "end_time": 271635.0,
      "text": "the advantages and incidental"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 271635.0,
      "end_time": 273646.0,
      "text": "costs of Smith’s ideas:"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 273646.0,
      "end_time": 275582.0,
      "text": "the price of corn dropped sharply,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 275582.0,
      "end_time": 276734.0,
      "text": "food became cheaper"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 276734.0,
      "end_time": 277906.0,
      "text": "and everyone, especially"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 277906.0,
      "end_time": 279064.0,
      "text": "the working classes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 279064.0,
      "end_time": 280367.0,
      "text": "had a lot more spare money"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 280367.0,
      "end_time": 282020.0,
      "text": "to spend on other goods,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 282020.0,
      "end_time": 283083.0,
      "text": "This, in turn"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 283083.0,
      "end_time": 284456.0,
      "text": "grew the overall size of the"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 284456.0,
      "end_time": 285357.0,
      "text": "British economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 285357.0,
      "end_time": 287557.0,
      "text": "so that it significantly outperformed"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 287557.0,
      "end_time": 289949.0,
      "text": "all of its European counterparts."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 289949.0,
      "end_time": 292538.0,
      "text": "But – and it was a very big but"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 292538.0,
      "end_time": 294779.0,
      "text": "large swathes of British agriculture"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 294779.0,
      "end_time": 296104.0,
      "text": "went to the wall."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 296104.0,
      "end_time": 297551.0,
      "text": "Cheap imported corn, from"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 297551.0,
      "end_time": 299109.0,
      "text": "Canada and the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 299109.0,
      "end_time": 300324.0,
      "text": "destroyed farms"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 300324.0,
      "end_time": 303496.0,
      "text": "and ways of life that had persisted for centuries."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 303496.0,
      "end_time": 305544.0,
      "text": "Smith’s theories were both correct"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 305544.0,
      "end_time": 307887.0,
      "text": "and, depending on where one was standing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 307887.0,
      "end_time": 310360.0,
      "text": "plainly agonizing."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 310360.0,
      "end_time": 312518.0,
      "text": "An enduring problem for the undoubtedly very"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 312518.0,
      "end_time": 315404.0,
      "text": "sound arguments in favour of free trade"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 315404.0,
      "end_time": 317129.0,
      "text": "is that its human costs"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 317129.0,
      "end_time": 318416.0,
      "text": "have seldom been addressed"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 318416.0,
      "end_time": 319679.0,
      "text": "with sufficient passion"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 319679.0,
      "end_time": 320950.0,
      "text": "and ingenuity."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 320950.0,
      "end_time": 322682.0,
      "text": "The cries of the dispossessed"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 322682.0,
      "end_time": 325318.0,
      "text": "have not been recognised for what they are:"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 325318.0,
      "end_time": 327440.0,
      "text": "threats to the entire stability"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 327440.0,
      "end_time": 329769.0,
      "text": "and moral dignity of a nation."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 329769.0,
      "end_time": 331962.0,
      "text": "As has only gradually been realised,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 331962.0,
      "end_time": 333940.0,
      "text": "the benefits of an open economy"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 333940.0,
      "end_time": 335935.0,
      "text": "can only properly bear fruit"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 335935.0,
      "end_time": 338690.0,
      "text": "if a series of steps are taken to mitigate"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 338690.0,
      "end_time": 341137.0,
      "text": "the attendant downsides."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 341137.0,
      "end_time": 343108.0,
      "text": "Any nation committed to free trade"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 343108.0,
      "end_time": 345444.0,
      "text": "must tax the sectors of the economy"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 345444.0,
      "end_time": 346914.0,
      "text": "which have an advantage"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 346914.0,
      "end_time": 348542.0,
      "text": "and then use the money"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 348542.0,
      "end_time": 350170.0,
      "text": "to retrain those in the"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 350170.0,
      "end_time": 351412.0,
      "text": "sectors of the economy"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 351412.0,
      "end_time": 353533.0,
      "text": "with the gravest disadvantages"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 353533.0,
      "end_time": 355781.0,
      "text": "in relation to foreign competition."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 355781.0,
      "end_time": 358593.0,
      "text": "Without such redirection of money and labor"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 358593.0,
      "end_time": 360198.0,
      "text": "a nation will become highly"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 360198.0,
      "end_time": 361675.0,
      "text": "unstable politically"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 361675.0,
      "end_time": 362994.0,
      "text": "thereby endangering"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 362994.0,
      "end_time": 365743.0,
      "text": "any progress that free trade has made."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 365743.0,
      "end_time": 367635.0,
      "text": "Secondly, governments must enable"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 367635.0,
      "end_time": 368906.0,
      "text": "everyone in the economy"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 368906.0,
      "end_time": 371511.0,
      "text": "to find their own natural areas of strength;"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 371511.0,
      "end_time": 374228.0,
      "text": "which means high levels of investment in education"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 374228.0,
      "end_time": 377843.0,
      "text": "and a raft of measures to maximize social mobility."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 377843.0,
      "end_time": 380060.0,
      "text": "Monopolistic behaviour by the rich"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 380060.0,
      "end_time": 383079.0,
      "text": "endangers the integrity of a free trade system"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 383079.0,
      "end_time": 386773.0,
      "text": "just as much as punitive import tariffs."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 386773.0,
      "end_time": 388702.0,
      "text": "Intellectually, free trade has"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 388702.0,
      "end_time": 391103.0,
      "text": "undoubtedly won the argument."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 391103.0,
      "end_time": 392956.0,
      "text": "When a Mexican worker can make a car"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 392956.0,
      "end_time": 394392.0,
      "text": "for eight dollars an hour,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 394392.0,
      "end_time": 395910.0,
      "text": "whereas an American one"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 395910.0,
      "end_time": 397706.0,
      "text": "costs 58 dollars an hour,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 397706.0,
      "end_time": 399922.0,
      "text": "it is clearly wise to allow Mexico"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 399922.0,
      "end_time": 402155.0,
      "text": "to do what it can do best,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 402155.0,
      "end_time": 405015.0,
      "text": "whatever the effect on American car workers."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 405015.0,
      "end_time": 407271.0,
      "text": "However, defenders of free trade"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 407271.0,
      "end_time": 408677.0,
      "text": "have been grossly negligent"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 408677.0,
      "end_time": 410282.0,
      "text": "when it comes to instituting"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 410282.0,
      "end_time": 412340.0,
      "text": "the political programs necessary"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 412340.0,
      "end_time": 413849.0,
      "text": "to support the efficient"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 413849.0,
      "end_time": 415620.0,
      "text": "operations of the system."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 415620.0,
      "end_time": 417194.0,
      "text": "It has forgotten the pain"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 417194.0,
      "end_time": 418322.0,
      "text": "of the car workers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 418322.0,
      "end_time": 420634.0,
      "text": "the coal miners and the steel makers."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 420634.0,
      "end_time": 422032.0,
      "text": "And, in democracies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 422032.0,
      "end_time": 423533.0,
      "text": "there has been a heavy price"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 423533.0,
      "end_time": 425003.0,
      "text": "to pay for this neglect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 425003.0,
      "end_time": 426640.0,
      "text": "in the form of the rise of a new"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 426640.0,
      "end_time": 428246.0,
      "text": "class of mercantilists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 428246.0,
      "end_time": 429819.0,
      "text": "who have successfully argued that"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 429819.0,
      "end_time": 432353.0,
      "text": "barriers must again increase,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 432353.0,
      "end_time": 433798.0,
      "text": "that a country should try to make"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 433798.0,
      "end_time": 435411.0,
      "text": "everything within its own borders"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 435411.0,
      "end_time": 436922.0,
      "text": "to regain its greatness"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 436922.0,
      "end_time": 438368.0,
      "text": "and that cheap importers"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 438368.0,
      "end_time": 439780.0,
      "text": "are invariably the"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 439780.0,
      "end_time": 442095.0,
      "text": "destroyers of domestic jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 442095.0,
      "end_time": 444255.0,
      "text": "These arguments make no sense,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 444255.0,
      "end_time": 447203.0,
      "text": "but so long as the proponents of free trade"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 447203.0,
      "end_time": 449674.0,
      "text": "fail properly to articulate a program"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 449674.0,
      "end_time": 452493.0,
      "text": "to remedy free trade’s operations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 452493.0,
      "end_time": 454313.0,
      "text": "whole nations will be seduced by the"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 454313.0,
      "end_time": 456530.0,
      "text": "easy promises of the mercantilists"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 456530.0,
      "end_time": 458459.0,
      "text": "and will suffer accordingly"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 458459.0,
      "end_time": 460551.0,
      "text": "until the distinctive wisdom"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 460551.0,
      "end_time": 462782.0,
      "text": "of Adam Smith can once more"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 462782.0,
      "end_time": 472782.0,
      "text": "reassert itself."
    }
  ]
}